INSERT INTO events (
                id,
                target_id,
                target_id_type,
                triggerer_id,
                triggerer_id_type,
                event_type,
                metadata
            )
            SELECT * FROM UNNEST (
                $1::bigint[],
                $2::bigint[],
                $3::text[],
                $4::bigint[],
                $5::text[],
                $6::text[],
                $7::jsonb[]
            )
